  "keyFeatures": [
    "Plugin framework with hot-loading and dependency injection",
    "ImGui-based UI system for in-game overlays and windows",
    "Comprehensive game state access (chat, targets, inventory, etc.)",
    "Inter-plugin communication via IPC CallGates",
    "Memory hooking and native interop with game internals",
    "Game data access via Lumina integration",
    "Event-driven architecture for game lifecycle hooks",
    "Command registration and chat integration"
